title: Naviator - GPS APP for pilots
description:
Naviator 3.7.3

Fully Cracked

Just sign up for the free trial using a real email address, then enjoy the full app for ever.



â€¢ GPS moving map with airspace, airports, radio navigation aids, airway intersections, TFRs

â€¢ All navigational data is downloaded to your device - no internet connection is required while you are flying

â€¢ Easy "rubber band" flight planning

â€¢ Support for ADS-B receivers including the iLevil AW/SW, Dual XGPS 170 and XGPS 190, Navworx, SkyGuardTWX, Flight Data Systems Pathfinder, Stratux and various receivers from FreeFlight Systems

â€¢ Integrates with ADS-B or the Zaon XRX for real-time traffic display

â€¢ NEW! AOPA members can import their stored routes from the AOPA Flight Planner

â€¢ NEW! Import custom airspace from OpenAir airspace files

â€¢ 3D synthetic vision with terrain, obstacles/towers and runways

â€¢ Global terrain database with terrain warnings

â€¢ Global Forecast Engine provides winds aloft anywhere on the planet up to 54,000 feet

â€¢ GPS track recording - upload your flight recordings to your own personalized Naviator Hangar (http://hangar.naviatorapp.com)

â€¢ Import routes from other flight planning systems using the GPX format

â€¢ Integrates with Microsoft Flight Simulator and Prepar3D

â€¢ Integrates with X-Plane using the "X-Plane to GPS" app (https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.appropel.xplanegps)

â€¢ Get a weather briefing and file a flight plan from right inside the app

â€¢ Vertical navigation (VNAV) calculator

â€¢ Canadian data including airspace, airports, navaids, terrain and weather

â€¢ NMEA output - Naviator can drive your aircraft's autopilot

â€¢ "Bring Your Own Charts" - you can import custom maps and charts into the app. See our forum for more details
